data.description: Are you looking for a cozy home in Pinetop? Look no further. This site-built property has brand new appliances, new base boards on the main level, and bathroom upstairs, all new flooring and carpet, new interior paint, all new blinds throughout the house with new windows in the Arizona room and upstairs bedroom front windows. This house even has brand new concrete patio pad to entertain family and friends. That's not all! There are new exterior concrete steps at the front. With new concrete apron at the garage entrance and front door entrance. The garage has epoxy flooring with a new garage door. The exterior of the house was just recently repainted.
